author: maintainer-agent
resolution: Deduplicated private Levenshtein implementations onto the shared bounded OSA helper.
expected_result: Item-id and extension-capability suggestions share the same typo-distance primitive.
actual_result: Private copies were removed and focused helper/extension tests plus coverage passed.
